<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>torch::PackedTensorAccessor64&lt;scalar_t,<sp/>1,<sp/>torch::RestrictPtrTraits&gt;<sp/>px</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">)<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>const<sp/>unsigned<sp/>int<sp/>idx<sp/>=<sp/>blockIdx.x<sp/>*<sp/>blockDim.x<sp/>+<sp/>threadIdx.x;<sp/>///&lt;<sp/>Calculate<sp/>unique<sp/>thread<sp/>index.</highlight></codeline>
